2) 'Photograph of the Prince and Princess of Wales in an open carriage (officer saluting), leaving the Quadrangle of Windsor Castle'.

4) 'Photograph of the nave of St George's Chapel, Windsor, looking west, with the fittings used at the wedding of the Prince of Wales'.

5) 'Photograph of interior of the bride's chamber at St George's Chapel, Windows, shwoing the dressing table, looking glass, etcetera'.
